# 9. VLAN 설정

## VLAN 생성

```bash
vlan 100
name Management

vlan 200
name Marketing

vlan 300
name Informain
```

---

## Access Port

```bash
interface fa0/2
switchport mode access
switchport access vlan 100
```

---

## Trunk Port

```bash
interface fa0/1
switchport mode trunk
```

---

# 10. Router-on-a-Stick (Sub Interface)

## 개념
라우터 하나의 인터페이스로 여러 VLAN을 라우팅하는 기술이다.

---

## 설정

```bash
interface gig0/0
no ip address
no shutdown

interface gig0/0.100
encapsulation dot1q 100
ip address 192.168.100.254 255.255.255.0

interface gig0/0.200
encapsulation dot1q 200
ip address 192.168.200.254 255.255.255.0

interface gig0/0.300
encapsulation dot1q 300
ip address 192.168.250.254 255.255.255.0
```

---

# 11. EIGRP 재분배 (Redistribution)

## 개념
서로 다른 라우팅 프로토콜 간 경로 정보를 교환하는 기술이다.

---

## 설정

```bash
router eigrp 10
redistribute eigrp 20 metric 1000 100 255 1 1500
no auto-summary

router eigrp 20
redistribute eigrp 10 metric 1000 100 255 1 1500
no auto-summary
```

---

